      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed in mint condition \u2014 and we mean it. This is a truly exceptional example that stands apart from typical used car listings. The exterior is flawless, with paint that shines like new, no scratches, dents, chips, or blemishes of any kind. Every panel is straight and true, and the trim and glass are in perfect shape. Step inside and you'll find an interior that looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor \u2014 the seats, carpets, headliner, and all surfaces are spotless and show virtually no signs of wear. All electronics, controls, and features function perfectly. Under the hood, the engine is clean, well-maintained, and runs beautifully, with no leaks, unusual noises, or warning lights. The tires have excellent tread remaining and the brakes are in great shape. This is the kind of used car that is genuinely difficult to find \u2014 a vehicle that has been meticulously cared for throughout its life. Buyers who want a used car with zero compromises should look no further.",
