    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly exceptional, mint condition \u2014 a rare find in the used car market. The exterior is virtually flawless, with a deep, lustrous paint finish free of scratches, dents, or blemishes of any kind. Every panel aligns perfectly, and the chrome and trim pieces shine as if the car just rolled off the showroom floor. The interior is equally impressive: the upholstery, dashboard, carpeting, and all surfaces are spotless and show virtually no signs of use or wear. All mechanical systems \u2014 engine, transmission, brakes, suspension, and electronics \u2014 operate perfectly, with no known issues whatsoever. Service records are up to date, and the car has been meticulously maintained throughout its life. If you're looking for a used vehicle that feels and looks essentially new, this is it. Serious buyers will not be disappointed.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition at $34,000, and that price reflects an honest, accurate assessment of what you're getting. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 the paint retains good color and shine, though you'll notice minor scratches and light wear consistent with regular use. There are no major dents or rust concerns, and the body panels are straight. The interior is clean and functional, showing normal signs of use such as light wear on high-contact surfaces like the steering wheel and seat bolsters, but nothing that detracts significantly from comfort or appearance. Mechanically, this car has been maintained and runs reliably \u2014 the engine starts cleanly, the transmission shifts smoothly, and all major systems are in working order. You may encounter minor items that could use attention over time, as is typical with a used vehicle, but nothing that should concern a buyer looking for a dependable, solid car. Overall, this is a well-rounded used vehicle that offers genuine value for the price.",
